       National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration Current Events

   OSEI severe weather products (SVR) include multichannel color composite
   imagery and animations of severe thunderstorms or thunderstorm
   complexes as seen from both polar (N4, N5) and geostationary (G8, G10)
   satellites

      The following image files have recently been added to the Severe
